OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSocial care: Immigration   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frules to be relaxed to     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frecruit staff              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Immigration rules are to be temporarily
OL,6, relaxed for overseas care workers in a 
OL,7, bid to recruit and keep staff, the     
OL,8, government has announced.              
OL,10,FSocial care workers, care assistants   
OL,11,Fand home care workers are to become    
OL,12,Feligible for a health and care visa for
OL,13,Fa 12-month period.                     
OL,15,FThe government said this would make it 
OL,16,Feasier to fill gaps in workforces.     
OL,18,FIt followed warnings the sector faced  
OL,19,F"severe and increasing" problems with  
OL,20,Fhiring and keeping staff after Brexit. 
